  <bioghist id="aspace_c81fae6f6f3215ed4f1ee153dac6f188">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Verdi Burtch was an ornithologist in Penn Yan, Yates County, New York.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_213665cbb110cdd1740575d404738d0f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
